==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Lacklustre
<hw>Lack"lus`tre</hw> }</mhw>
<pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Wanting luster or brightness.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Lackluster</xex> eye.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Lacking spirit, liveliness, or enthusiasm;
dull.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Mediocre; <as>as, a <ex>lackluster</ex>
performance</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lacmus</ent>⟦br⟧
